  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the diagnostic performance of two-dimensional shear-wave elastography (SWE) for
      staging hepatic fibrosis in the background liver parenchyma in patients with liver tumors
      before hepatic resection, using resected tissue pathology as a reference standard.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
